message: Hey Sarah, how's my progress looking?
You're still on track to hit your exercise goals, but let's work on sticking to the meal plan. What do you think about trying some new recipes this week?

Yeah, I know it's been tough to stick to the diet lately. Any tips for making healthy meals more exciting?

Hey Rohan! Yes, meal prep can be a game-changer. Just make sure to vary your protein sources and veggies.
That sounds doable. Thanks for the advice!
Rohan, just a heads up that your blood pressure has been a bit higher than usual this week. Let's discuss some stress-reducing techniques at our next call, okay?
Stress is definitely an issue. I'll work on prioritizing self-care.
Great job, Rohan! Remember to take breaks and stretch during your business trip this week. We've got a few tips on staying healthy while traveling if you need them.

Thanks, Advik! I'll make sure to stay on top of it.
Rohan, have you been taking your meds consistently? We noticed a slight dip in your levels this week.
Don't worry, Neel, we're on it! Rohan, can you confirm whether you took your meds as scheduled?

Hey Rohan! Have you heard about the benefits of turmeric for heart health? Worth exploring
Remember to take your meds on time today, Rohan!

Hey Rohan, how's your blood pressure been this week?

Remember to stretch before bed and after exercise! Helps with blood flow
Good reminder Ruby Thanks for the tip! Did you get the full diagnostic test panel done?

Great job on taking proactive steps Rohan Remember to adjust your diet accordingly

Consistency is key Rohan Try to schedule it in your calendar and stick to it

Don't worry, we've got you covered Rohan Keep your meds and supplements with you and try to stick to your routine as much as possible
Hey Sarah, how's my blood sugar control looking?

Hi Rohan! Remember to take your metformin at the same time every day, and try to stay hydrated!

Rohan, I'm concerned about your exercise routine. You've only been consistent 3 days this week. Can we reschedule your workout schedule?
Yeah, sorry Sarah. Been busy with work. Can we push my next appointment to Friday instead?
